### Get All Service Types
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/service-types/

### Create Service Type
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/service-types/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Oil Change",
  "description": "Regular oil change service",
  "basePrice": 50.00,
  "durationMinutes": 30
}

### Get Service Type by ID
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/service-types/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### Update Service Type
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/v1/service-types/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Oil Change Updated",
  "description": "Updated oil change service",
  "basePrice": 55.00,
  "durationMinutes": 35
}